  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man who hunted a deer with a chainsaw was arrested in Putthalam",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person has been arrested on suspicion of hunting a deer and selling it for meat in the Puttalam Vannathivillu area by the officials of the Wildlife Department on the 2nd of Saturday afternoon.",
        "A person who hunted deer with a bandana and sold the meat has been arrested by the Karulakasveva Wildlife Department.",
        "A deer horn and a deer skin were seized during a search conducted around the area based on confidential information received by the Wildlife Department officials that deer meat was being sold.",
        "Karulakaswewa Wildlife Department Officer Marasingha said that they are continuing to investigate the arrested suspect.",
        "He said that steps have been taken to produce the arrested suspect and the body parts of the deer in the Puttalam court."
      ],
